#merge sort:
Merge Sort is a divide-and-conquer algorithm that divides an array into smaller parts
, sorts them, and then merges them into a sorted array.


# quick sor:
Quick Sort is a divide-and-conquer algorithm that selects a pivot element and partitions
 the array so that smaller elements are on the left and larger elements are on the right